---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import cover from "~/assets/covers/top-cover.png";
import whyUsImage from "~/assets/why-us.png";
---

<section class="bg-bg px-edge py-10 lg:py-20 relative">
  <Image
    class="absolute left-0 top-0 right-0"
    quality={100}
    src={cover}
    alt="cover"
  />

  <div
    class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto relative z-10 flex gap-10 flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between"
  >
    <Image src={whyUsImage} alt="personal trainer tristain" />
    <div class="max-w-xl text-center lg:text-right">
      <p class="font-oswald text-2xl">Why TWR Fitness?</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 font-oswald font-bold text-4xl text-text-dark">
        Unleashing <span class="text-primary-lighter">Your Full Potential</span>
        Is at the Core of <span class="text-primary-lighter">What I Do!</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg">
        This company, my career, was born of the idea that the greatest pursuit
        in life is to chase the potential that we all possess. a potential we
        may never truly realize, but that, to me, is the pointâ€¦ to continually
        strive to be better than the day before despite our obstacles, to see
        what we are capable of when we are dedicated, and then to watch as we
        move forward with passion and enthusiasm and all the pieces fall into
        place.
      </p>
      <p class="italic">Chase Your Potential</p>
      <p>- Tristan W. Roveto, Founder of TWR Fitness</p>
      <a
        href="/your-fitness-journey"
        class="mt-7 bg-accent py-5 px-6 rounded text-white font-bold inline-block"
        >Start Your Fitness Journey For Free</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
